{"tid":2157578,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民建聯 社團 涉藉採樣套料  疑誤導與民政總署有關 街坊憂種票","createTime":"2020-08-15T06:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T06:27:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5262a022952c377b8fb9de1d8c455c3826067305","tid":2157578,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:27:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/ABX6QVH3ZBHHDCNLEUWYUMLKC4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FABX6QVH3ZBHHDCNLEUWYUMLKC4%2F&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8QVsaiM9baN%2FEtUhsAXiQ7E%3D&h=df24862c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FABX6QVH3ZBHHDCNLEUWYUMLKC4%2F&h=ba665e9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/ABX6QVH3ZBHHDCNLEUWYUMLKC4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n民建聯 社團 涉藉採樣套料 <br />\n疑誤導與民政總署有關 街坊憂種票<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【武肺再爆發】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：播毒一個月 慶回歸婦終確診<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港府日前宣。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，會員須提供電話及住址登記報名；另有石蔭區街坊亦收到疑由民建聯發出的招募全民檢測義工訊息，令人以為核酸檢測及義工招募與民政事務總署有關。不過，署方否認與相關團體合作，居民質疑相關團體涉誤導，擔心被套取個人資料作種票等其他用途。<br />\n<br />\n葵盛東、西邨居民近日收到香。。。。。。。。。。。訊息表明「報名時請報上姓名，電話，住宅地址，以作登記記錄。歡迎同住家庭成員一同參加&hellip;&hellip;詳細情形稍後公佈。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：九龍醫院護士中招 同事隔離<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tu8QJkQT0EoEVE6qo9KF-BRA1A0=/1182x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BOUDI7KVJBG3FNUQD43GSTK7CA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ftu8QJkQT0EoEVE6qo9KF-BRA1A0%3D%2F1182x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBOUDI7KVJBG3FNUQD43GSTK7CA.jpg&h=ae95b3c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■參與招募義工的郭玲麗是民建聯社區幹事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n居民以為做會員才可參加<br />\n<br />\n葵青區議員梁靜珊批評，。。。。。。。。。。「唔知道佢哋（聯誼會）會唔會藉檢測有其他意圖」。<br />\n<br />\n涉事聯誼會隸屬於香港廣西社團總會。本報記者透過WhatsApp。。。。。。。。。。。。居民需取樽交唾液樣本，換言之並非「咽拭子採樣」。<br />\n<br />\n對於WhatsApp訊息被指誤導居民，聯誼會人士反駁指有人斷章取義，甚至指是用作所謂種票之用，是誣揑及歪曲事實，會保留法律追究權利。記者致電訊息中提及的一個電話號碼，接聽電話。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n招義工地點為陳恒鑌議辦<br />\n<br />\n此外，石蔭區街坊亦收到疑由民建聯發出的WhatsApp訊息，指民政總署將進行大規模社區檢測計劃，招募義工負責派發樣本瓶。<br />\n<br />\n訊息顯示首名報名的義工正是民建聯社區幹事郭玲麗，而義工集合地點是「石蔭路辦事處門口」，該處是民建聯立法會議員陳恒鑌其中一個辦事處。接獲居民求助的葵青區議員林紹輝質疑，石籬石蔭區不在社區檢測計劃內，義工招募訊息有誤導之嫌。陳恒鑌及郭玲麗至截稿前未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n民政事務總署稱，社。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/aGse5dRiJ8fJIujYh-ccPpZaBys=/861x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FGL2Y5DO5VCARAIT6LNU2AGWGY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FaGse5dRiJ8fJIujYh-ccPpZaBys%3D%2F861x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFGL2Y5DO5VCARAIT6LNU2AGWGY.jpg&h=78514f19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有葵青居民收到同鄉會短訊稱可檢測武肺，提及民政總署檢測計劃。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mA7_ThQ2enfYUaJMC5U-7B4QEbI=/811x1068/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U2Q7ODJ3IZGCTJKKYW3TFIFGSM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmA7_ThQ2enfYUaJMC5U-7B4QEbI%3D%2F811x1068%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU2Q7ODJ3IZGCTJKKYW3TFIFGSM.jpg&h=a3292be4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■民建聯疑似向石蔭居民招募檢測義工，報名人包括郭玲麗（紅框示）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IzJrJPEd5shBKTi2ZRdB4a_Rohw=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/S6Y44BLL4VB5TC3RT66LO3IHMQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIzJrJPEd5shBKTi2ZRdB4a_Rohw%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FS6Y44BLL4VB5TC3RT66LO3IHMQ.jpg&h=0f41f101&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■政府近日在慈雲山等地派發咽喉拭子採樣套裝，但未擴展至葵盛邨及石蔭邨。資料圖片"}]}